<h2>Filtering</h2>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-3">

<p>If <strong>positive</strong> condition:</p>

<ul data-wb-json='{
		"url": "demo/data-en.json#/anArray",
		"queryall": "li",
		"mapping": [
			"/name"
		],
		"filter": [
			{ "path": "/prop", "value": "blue" }
		]

	}'>
	<template>
		<li></li>
	</template>
</ul>


</div>


<div class="col-md-3">

<p>If <strong>negative</strong> condition:</p>

<ul data-wb-json='{
		"url": "demo/data-en.json#/anArray",
		"queryall": "li",
		"mapping": [
			"/name"
		],
		"filternot": [
			{ "path": "/prop", "value": "blue" }
		]

	}'>
	<template>
		<li></li>
	</template>
</ul>


</div>


<div class="col-md-6">

<p>Combinaison of both condition:</p>

